Zagorski ChM Ltd is a bulgarian company founded in 1996. With more than 25 years of experience in various fields of online measuring systems and industrial automation for various applications in different industrial fields, Zagorski ChM Ltd could offer the best solution for a specific measurement task.
The company collaborates with world-renowned producers and suppliers of technical equipment such as:
FLEXIM (Germany) - a leader in the field of clamp-on ultrasonic flow measurement;
SWAN ANALYTICAL INSTRUMENTS (Switzerland) - a pioneering technology provider of online water quality measuring analytical systems;
MICHELL INSTRUMENTS (United Kingdom) - an international leader in high-precision sensing specializing in instrumentation for dew point, relative humidity and oxygen analysis;
ENOTEC - manufacturer of gas analyzers for process and for CEMS, resulting in minimized energy consumption, reduced emissions and optimal process control;
SIGRIST-PHOTOMETER (Switzerland) - manufacturer of high quality process photometers;
SENTRY EQUIPMENT (United States) - a leader in the field of representative sampling and analysis;
PARTECH (United Kingdom) - manufacturer of drinking water and wastewater measurement equipment;
BW TECHNOLOGY (United Kingdom) - manufacturer of gas analyser systems;
WATERSAM (Germany) - manufacturer of water sampling systems;
LASER DIAGNOSTIC INSTRUMENTS (Estonia) - manufacturer of  non-contact sensors that detect oil on water and Spectral Fluorescence Signatures Analyzers to detect and analyze fingerprints of compounds;
ATEK (Turkey) - manufacturer of encoders, temperature and pressure transmitters.
Zagorski ChM Ltd also provides various services in the field of equipment repair, troubleshooting, analysis of existing measuring systems, ultrasonic flow measurement of liquids and gases, etc. The team also has experience with creating various sampling and analytical systems and repairing old analytical equipment.

Reforma de Componentes e Equipamentos de Mineração e Construção;
