FMCC (Reliability Maintenance and Caledonian Design) Group is a consortium of companies aimed at improving the total cost of ownership of stationary and mobile industrial equipment.

Leveraging technical expertise and artificial intelligence, FMCC Group intervenes at every stage of the equipment lifecycle and client maintenance services:

- Client maintenance service audit;
- Development and implementation of maintenance strategies;
- Deployment of Computerized Maintenance Management Systems (CMMS);
- Definition of purchasing policies and inventory management;
- Monitoring of critical equipment;
- On-site intervention;
- Workshop reconditioning of components;
- Equipment testing with certification and warranty;
- Supply of spare parts.

FMCC Group's services cater to all companies utilizing industrial equipment fleets.

FMCC Group's values: Reliability - Innovation - Customer Service.

Why choose us: Expertise - Service quality - Strong partnerships with manufacturers - Warranty.

